    "We include an example document of this sort in the appendix of this paper (S1 Appendix), specifically for LLMs and based upon the rules given here.",
    "This document should advocate for ethical and inclusive use of these models in science and society.",
    "Remember, these rules provide general guidance, and it's important to adapt them to specific scientific disciplines and contexts.",
